<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>CaravanPi Konfiguration</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<meta name="google" content="notranslate" />
		<!-- Stylesheets -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/main.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/remote.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/custom.css">
		<!-- Icons -->
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="57x57" href="icons/apple-icon-57x57.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="60x60" href="icons/apple-icon-60x60.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="72x72" href="icons/apple-icon-72x72.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="76x76" href="icons/apple-icon-76x76.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114" href="icons/apple-icon-114x114.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="120x120" href="icons/apple-icon-120x120.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="144x144" href="icons/apple-icon-144x144.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="152x152" href="icons/apple-icon-152x152.png">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="icons/apple-icon-180x180.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192"  href="icons/android-icon-192x192.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="icons/favicon-32x32.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="96x96" href="icons/favicon-96x96.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="icons/favicon-16x16.png">
		<link rel="manifest" href="icons/manifest.json">
		<meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#ffffff">
		<meta name="msapplication-TileImage" content="icons/ms-icon-144x144.png">
		<meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="MagicRemote">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
		<meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container normal fill">
			<h3>CaravanPi Konfiguration</h3>
			
			<div class="config-block">
				<h4>Waage Gasflasche</h4>
				<form action="buttontest.py" method="post">
					<p for="startPositionCalibration">Kalibrierung Waage</p>
					<div class="helpmessage">
						<p>Bitte nehmen Sie vor der Kalibierung die Gssflasche von der Waage!<p>
						<p>Die Kalibierung erfolgt bei leerer Waage.<p>
					</div>
					<button type="submit" id="startScaleCalibration" name="startScaleCalibration" class="formbutton">Gaswaage kalibrieren!</button>
				</form>
	
				<form class="form-horizontal" action="writeConfig.py" method="post">

					<!-- Form Name -->

					<!-- Multiple Radios -->
					  <label class="text" for="gasTara">Leergewicht Gasflasche</label>
					  <div class="col-md-4">
					  <div class="radio">
						<label for="gasTara-0">
						  <input type="radio" name="gasTara" id="gasTara-0" value="1" checked="checked">
						  5,0 kg (Alu 6 kg Flasche)
						</label>
						</div>
					  <div class="radio">
						<label for="gasTara-1">
						  <input type="radio" name="gasTara" id="gasTara-1" value="2">
						  5,3 kg (Alu 11 kg Flasche)
						</label>
						</div>
					  <div class="radio">
						<label for="gasTara-2">
						  <input type="radio" name="gasTara" id="gasTara-2" value="3">
						  7 kg (Stahl 5 kg Flasche)
						</label>
						</div>
					  <div class="radio">
						<label for="gasTara-3">
						  <input type="radio" name="gasTara" id="gasTara-3" value="4">
						  12,5 kg (Stahl 11 kg Flasche)
						</label>
						</div>
					  </div>

					<!-- Text input-->
					  <label class="text" for="gastaratxt">freie Eingabe Leergewicht</label>  
					  <div class="">
						  <input id="gastaratxt" name="gastaratxt" type="number" placeholder="5" class="">
					  </div>

				</form>
			</div>
			
			<div class="config-block">
				<form action="buttontest.py" method="post">
					<p for="startPositionCalibration">Kalibrierung Lagesensor</p>
					<div class="helpmessage">
						<p>Voraussetzungen:<p>
						<p>- Der Wohnwagen steht in Längs- und Querrichtung waagrecht<p>
						<p>- Es befinden sich keine Personen im Wohnwagen<p>
						<p>- Der Wohnwagen steht bereits seit mehreren Minuten unverändert (schwingt nicht nach)<p>
						<p></p>
						<p>Nach Auslösen der Kalibrierung wird weitere 2 Minuten gewartet. Piper und LED zeigen eigentliche Kalibrierung an.</p>
					</div>
					<button type="submit" id="startPositionCalibration" name="startPositionCalibration" class="formbutton">Lagesensor kalibrieren!</button>
				</form>

				<form class="form-horizontal" action="writeConfig.py" method="post">

					<!-- Form Name -->

					<!-- Multiple Radios -->
					<!-- Text input-->
					  <label class="" for="tolx">Toleranz X</label>  
					  <div class="">
					  <input id="tolx" name="tolx" type="number" placeholder="0" class="form-control input-md">
					  </div>

					<!-- Text input-->
					  <label class="" for="toly">ToleranzY</label>  
					  <div class="">
					  <input id="toly" name="toly" type="number" placeholder="0" class="form-control input-md">
					  </div>

					<!-- Text input-->
					  <label class="" for="approxx">Approx X</label>  
					  <div class="">
					  <input id="approxx" name="approxx" type="number" placeholder="0" class="form-control input-md">
					  </div>

					<!-- Text input-->
					  <label class="" for="approxy">Approx Y</label>  
					  <div class="">
					  <input id="approxy" name="approxy" type="number" placeholder="0" class="form-control input-md">
					  </div>

					<!-- Button -->
					  <label class="" for="send">Senden</label>
					  <div class="">
						<button type="submit" id="submit" name="submit" class="btn btn-default">Konfiguration speichern</button>
					  </div>
				</form>
			</div>


		</div>
	</body>
</html>